/>\n其他冇幫襯過。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買咩有兩舊水咁抵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係&ldquo;檢查費&ldquo;200，問題係之後個維修費用我買過架仲有找。"},{"pid":"afbbf7d617a870ae65ddba1305a1f92e4aa768f6","tid":51620,"uid":18465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T09:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n伏左兩舊水算囉，冇下次姐。<br />\n<br />\n我又唔覺得日本天皇正常得過佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他冇幫襯過。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買咩有兩舊水咁抵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係&ldquo;檢查費&ldquo;200，問題係之後個維修費用我買過架仲有找。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留返做紙鎮算啦"},{"pid":"ae9ecd78971b8e594caecd2a0e99769c85ca3f15","tid":51620,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n伏左兩舊水算囉，冇下次姐。<br />\n<br />\n我又唔覺得日本天皇正常得過佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他冇幫襯過。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買咩有兩舊水咁抵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係&ldquo;檢查費&ldquo;200，問題係之後個維修費用我買過架仲有找。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n留返做紙鎮算啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係。多得佢激起我去搵資料自己學，結果只用少量工具整得番。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多謝遊樂場。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8881bde25f507921a8f25d6c292510daf65208fd","tid":51620,"uid":65495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n伏左兩舊水算囉，冇下次姐。<br />\n<br />\n我又唔覺得日本天皇正常得過佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他冇幫襯過。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買咩有兩舊水咁抵</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係&ldquo;檢查費&ldquo;200，問題係之後個維修費用我買過架仲有找。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n檢查費真係搵水魚。 檢完 ， 開個價貴過部機。<br />\n唔整-&gt;收$200<br />\n整-&gt;仲慘<br />\n可能check都無check，即收兩舊"},{"pid":"318172cefe209efaab961ec280a936f8e5b33308","tid":51620,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T18:10:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係&ldquo;檢查費&ldquo;200，問題係之後個維修費用我買過架仲有找。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n檢查費真係搵水魚。 檢完 ， 開個價貴過部機。<br />\n唔整-&gt;收$200<br />\n整-&gt;仲慘<br />\n可能check都無check，即收兩舊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n檢查費我明白：鬼叫你唔識整，我預左。<br />\n<br />\n但之後果個價係我買過架有找呢。<br />\n<br />\n激發左我去學囉結果。機械式相機只要故障唔涉及電子部分，還可以。<br />\n(果次係電子野，但只是replace就可以)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反而搵parts難過整，但貴極都一定唔係等於/大於買過架。"},{"pid":"5502a3841e0b81cdea8eef32cf9e733a6373c33c","tid":51620,"uid":5469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T19:17:52.000Z","msg":"推到黑店收檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c633f4b4c95d773e8539fe93c830f0879e5f52","tid":51620,"uid":36489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:25:41.000Z","msg":"沖片差撚到仆街"},{"pid":"df99ad742712f33801b3b5377ae0bcf026bfd674","tid":51620,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T05:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推到黑店收檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇佢我又唔會的起心肝學整機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6628ce9fe944fa7b7f70b9ad26c07f23b44ea67","tid":51620,"uid":65495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T12:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kin44x7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKin44x7.jpg&h=2ee23611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有&quot;伏&quot;袋抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3156c11f857f84373120f3f20414b00521a6f1","tid":51620,"uid":62971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T12:19:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kin44x7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKin44x7.jpg